  "detailed_description": "<strong>Shady Part of Me</strong> sends you on an emotional and dream-like journey, with breathtaking artistic direction and the enthralling voice of Hannah Murray (Game of Thrones, Skins).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/4dfb357057175a57eed5e81adcfac145.poster.avif?t=1727793514\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/4dfb357057175a57eed5e81adcfac145.webm?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/4dfb357057175a57eed5e81adcfac145.mp4?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a little girl and her shadow, overcome emotional struggles through surreal dreamscapes across a touching narrative filled with twists and surprises. Both must learn, cooperate and evolve to progress in a poetic journey. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with light and shadows, switching between 2D and 3D gameplay at will<br></li><li>Your ability to rewind time will help you get you through all situations<br></li><li>Explore surreal environments envisioned in a unique watercolor style<br></li><li>Solve contemplative puzzles to break the dream<br></li><li>Experience an introspective narrative journey like no other</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/7a47a4f18f71bf2a210345e8ccaa0a2e.poster.avif?t=1727793514\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/7a47a4f18f71bf2a210345e8ccaa0a2e.webm?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/7a47a4f18f71bf2a210345e8ccaa0a2e.mp4?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Shady Part of Me</strong> sends you on an emotional and dream-like journey, with breathtaking artistic direction and the enthralling voice of Hannah Murray (Game of Thrones, Skins).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/4dfb357057175a57eed5e81adcfac145.poster.avif?t=1727793514\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/4dfb357057175a57eed5e81adcfac145.webm?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/4dfb357057175a57eed5e81adcfac145.mp4?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As a little girl and her shadow, overcome emotional struggles through surreal dreamscapes across a touching narrative filled with twists and surprises. Both must learn, cooperate and evolve to progress in a poetic journey. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play with light and shadows, switching between 2D and 3D gameplay at will<br></li><li>Your ability to rewind time will help you get you through all situations<br></li><li>Explore surreal environments envisioned in a unique watercolor style<br></li><li>Solve contemplative puzzles to break the dream<br></li><li>Experience an introspective narrative journey like no other</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/7a47a4f18f71bf2a210345e8ccaa0a2e.poster.avif?t=1727793514\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/7a47a4f18f71bf2a210345e8ccaa0a2e.webm?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1116580/extras/7a47a4f18f71bf2a210345e8ccaa0a2e.mp4?t=1727793514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
